     "LR6 SO4 AO3: Lateral Rectus → CN VI (Abducens), Superior Oblique → CN IV (Trochlear), All Others → CN III (Oculomotor). Abducens nerve palsy: inability to abduct eye, diplopia on lateral gaze.",
