     "NADH → Complex I → CoQ → Complex III → Cyt c → Complex IV → O2. FADH2 → Complex II → CoQ → rest of chain. Complex I and II both feed electrons to CoQ. NADH produces ~2.5 ATP; FADH2 produces ~1.5 ATP.",
     "NADH→复合体I→CoQ→复合体III→细胞色素c→复合体IV→O2。FADH2→复合体II→CoQ。NADH产生约2.5 ATP，FADH2产生约1.5 ATP。",
